":"Rinko","body":"How she wants you and I to lead her... if she loses her way...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event156-14-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"Ah, you mean what she said before the audition...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event156-14-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"I wasn't really doing it on purpose though...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event156-14-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"Even so, you always show us things in a different light. That is why I asked this of you.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event156-14-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"Yes... Ako-chan is always straightforward...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event156-14-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":25}],"windowDisplayName":"Rinko","body":"And you also... have the \"dark walker\" skill... Right...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":25,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":25,"voiceId":"event156-14-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":24}],"windowDisplayName":"Ako","body":"Yeah...! I'm happy if I've been of some help to you, Yukina-san!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":24,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":24,"voiceId":"event156-14-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"Yes, you have. Thanks to you, we were also able to prepare a new song.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"event156-14-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect